      "data/authority/rkpc_terminal_fix_register.csv",
      "data/authority/rkpc_sid_star_route_register.csv"
    ],
    "rules": [
      "STAR entry fix is the first named fix of a STAR route.",
      "SID exit fix is the final major outbound fix of an RNAV SID route, not the first SID fix.",
      "IPDAS and MAKET are conventional bidirectional gates and may be used for both inbound and outbound scenario traffic.",
      "LIMDI, TAMNA, IPDAS, and MAKET are overlapping gates and must keep both arrival/departure roles where applicable.",
      "RWY31 RNAV departure procedures are available only inside simulator RWY25+31 mode.",
      "For duplicated exit fixes in RWY25+31 mode, the runway-specific SID should be selected by procedure/runway context; exit-fix role remains common."
    ]
  },
